    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2005-02-17</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2005-03-10T19:49:23Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>More Money for College Act - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to: (1) eliminate the dollar limitation applicable to the tax deduction for qualified tuition and related expenses; (2) deny such deduction for taxpayers with adjusted gross incomes exceeding $80,000 ($160,000 for joint returns), adjusted for inflation; and (3) make such deduction permanent.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
